      "replayStartSec": 2.424169,
      "replayEndSec": 6.651448,
      "narrationText": "第一步。让我们导入现有的 rclone 配置。rclone 支持 S3、Backblaze、Google Drive、Dropbox 等众多服务，如果你已经在使用，可以直接导入同一份配置。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-01.a20da912.mp3",
      "textHash": "a20da912d12ad42d9ec57c6c136b3ab197fd4e53aad643d7f18cec06d39cb61c",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.00898,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-01-after.0d8e1904.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.989388,
      "afterTextHash": "0d8e19042b1813318fe980b48e68056df67b41a75c610450f6ed7736e48c2c18"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 6.651448,
      "replayEndSec": 10.354487,
      "narrationText": "让我们列出命令行工具现在已知的存储。每个存储都是我们可以推送备份的目标。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-02.af2bf87c.mp3",
      "textHash": "af2bf87c7956eaf2971615ffd5b909dc38761285824e2807c725bd6689480ba1",
      "audioDurationSec": 6.347755,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-02-after.ae9ace8b.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.970612,
      "afterTextHash": "ae9ace8b950ed304afa4de8f943bc3abcf227ffba64093fb1e65cc9cf23bf2c6"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 10.354487,
      "replayEndSec": 18.28182,
      "narrationText": "第二步。让我们推送一个完整备份。整个仓库，包括应用、数据库、文件和配置，全部上传。由于仓库本身是静态加密的，备份也是加密的，无需额外的密钥管理。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-03.70dbeca1.mp3",
      "textHash": "70dbeca190def8f2e7c987c49c3adeed82131ab0e47aebc516869f465644955e",
      "audioDurationSec": 16.666122,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-03-after.a250b728.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 5.32898,
      "afterTextHash": "a250b7282a14747f0d1b6adfc12c29d5ceca746b5dfa1cfcdd3ff801efcc5db0"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 18.28182,
      "replayEndSec": 26.532142,
      "narrationText": "让我们列出该存储上的可用备份。从这里开始，在全新服务器上恢复只需一条命令，即仓库拉取命令。相同的数据，相同的容器，不同的机器。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-04.c62a3ed7.mp3",
      "textHash": "c62a3ed770b84d6b5ee55a11245cb55f0d5e4f9bdb23edc96af1cdb16777fb94",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.635918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-04-after.c0575810.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.362449,
      "afterTextHash": "c05758109ce281877a9ede44696ac65597742b0d33acad73c35a802288488290"
    }
  ],
